Author: YIz
Title: [ANN][PRE-ICO] ðŸš€ The Ravn Korrax ICO â€“ Worldâ€™s first invisible chat app
Body: Welcome to the Ravn Korrax ICO!  Website | Whitepaper  Twitter | Medium | Reddit | Facebook | Telegram  Join the fully encrypted privacy, invisible stealth blockchain ecosystem.  Pre-Sale is Open!!   Quick Stats  Country of Origin: Dominican Republic Pre-Sale Start Date: June 7th 2018 Pre-Sale End Date: July 4th 2018 Total KRX Supply Pre Sale: 250.000.000 Token Sale Start Date: September 19th 2018 ICO price of token: 1 KRX / .05 USD Soft cap: None Hard cap: 192.307.692 KRX (max 9,615,385 USD)  *Any unsold KRX will be locked until January 2019 and will then go to the users growth fund.    FAQ's  When will KRX be listed on Exchanges? We will be working to list KRX on as many exchanges as possible. We are already in talks with a few exchanges.  How do I participate in Ravnâ€™s Korrax Pre Sale? The token generation event will be denominated at .05 cents $USD.  Stellar Lumens, Bitcoin and Ethereum will be accepted and converted at that time to reflect the pegged price.  By Clicking the ENTER ICO button, this will take you to your login portal where you can participate in the sale.    Where can I download the app? The Ravnapp chat platform is ready to use.  It can be downloaded on or before June 7th 2018, on both Android and iOS.  Can I use KRX from the presale within the app immediately? No. The RavnPay ecosystem is being built after the Pre Sale.  How much will KRX be worth one day? Use your imagination.   Is there a bounty program? This will be available after the presale moving into the main sale in September.
